snippet.title: Autobahn Police Simulator 2 - Official Trailer | PS4 | Aerosoft
snippet.description:
Official release: # 20.02.2020 #

Start your even more exciting career as law enforcer on Europe’s fastest road now with the successor to the popular Autobahn Police Simulator.

Available here: https://www.aerosoft.com/en/policerescue-simulation/police/2923/autobahn-police-simulator-2-ps4
